high_descs: Turn right and walk ahead, veering left to the coffee maker on the left side of the sink.
Pick up the lettuce on the counter.
Place the lettuce in the fridge, to the left of the apple. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Place the lettuce in the sink. to the right of the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled head of lettuce in a sink.

high_descs: Turn to the right. Then turn left to face the coffee machine.
Pick up the lettuce from in front of the coffee machine.
Hold the lettuce and move a few steps to the left and face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the lettuce inside. Shut the door and then open the door. Take out the lettuce and shut the door.
Hold the lettuce and turn to the right. Then turn left and face the sink.
Place the lettuce inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill a head of lettuce and place it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the coffee maker.
Pick up the lettuce from the counter.
Turn to the left and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the lettuce on the shelf, close the refrigerator. Open the refrigerator, remove the lettuce from the shelf, close the refrigerator.
Turn to the right and walk to the sink.
Place the lettuce into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place cold lettuce into a sink.
